'''Torr Snapit's starship''' was the [[Transport/Legends|transport]] in which [[Torr Snapit]] took [[Sladak]], [[Slatka]], [[Darth Zannah/Legends|Rain]], [[Hardin|Bug]], and [[Darovit|Tomcat]] to the [[Ruusan system/Legends|Hoth's Brand system]]. It was shot down by [[Sith/Legends|Sith]] minions.<ref name="POD">''[[Darth Bane: Path of Destruction]]''</ref>

